    "For this, as explained in the methodology, we will contrast and compare those two networks throughout the time dimension, in particular computing the Mann-Whitney U significance test assuming the null hypothesis (H0) is that there is no difference between the journalists and disinformation actors groups.",
    "The results of these tests are presented next, according to the type of metrics being analyzed: connectivity and centrality (Sect.",
